There are limits to freedoms. For example you can't perform obscene speech, slander, seditious speach, or engage in speach that would cause reckless endangerment. If GWB is saying there needs to be further limits on our freedoms, well I disagree with that. However, there are necessary limits to our freedom that are defined by law.<br>
<br>
The problem is the law can be &quot;&quot;&quot;intrepeted&quot;&quot;&quot; by any moron with a license to practice law. Judges can place their views into interpreting the law also. A shitload of laws need to be more detailed and cover a broader scope so NO INTERPRETATION can be interjected. Start with Felony Murder and work your way down.<br>
